description:
Jokebot is a joke generation bot. It has a lot of jokes in it that's for sure.
The categories of jokes it has are varied. They are
Normal Jokes,Blonde Jokes,Dirty Jokes,Chuck Norris Jokes,Life Jokes,Computer / I.T Jokes,Money Jokes,Insult Jokes,Sarcastic Jokes.
In addition to, that you can Also ask it for a random joke which will give you a joke from any category,

You can simply ask it for jokes by saying.
"Alexa, Ask jokebot for anâ€‹ Insult Joke"
or
"Alexa, Ask Jokebot for a Joke"

Just ask it for your jokes, and fill your hearts' delight with humour
Disclaimer : This skill maybe not suited to audiences of all ages.
exampleInteractions: Alexa, Ask Jokebot for a Joke
Alexa, Ask jokebot for a Marriage Joke
Alexa, Ask Jokebot for a life joke

shortDescription:
